[hujan deras]

00:54:25.220 --> 00:54:28.766
[musik piano melankolis dimainkan]

00:54:44.990 --> 00:54:46.200
[menghela napas]

00:54:48.744 --> 00:54:50.662
Ya ampun, dasar berandalan.

00:54:50.746 --> 00:54:51.830
[suara kabel berdenting]

00:55:10.015 --> 00:55:11.725
[koper berdentuman]

00:55:17.689 --> 00:55:18.649
EKSPANSI LAYANAN IOT

00:55:18.732 --> 00:55:19.775
MENINGKATKAN SALURAN MITRA

00:55:22.945 --> 00:55:25.948
-[gemericik hujan]
-[musik melankolis terus berlanjut]

00:55:26.865 --> 00:55:27.950
[mengendus]

00:55:28.700 --> 00:55:29.993
